<section id="checkFormat">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>check formats</primary>
      <secondary>creating new</secondary>
    </indexterm>Check Format</title>
  <para>To add a new check format, select the <guilabel>NEW</guilabel> button.
  The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/checkFormat.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Create new Check Format</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When creating a new check format, you are presented with the following
  options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Name</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a name to describe the check format.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a description to further describe the check format.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Report</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Specify the report definition you want to associate with the
        check format.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
